io.spine.base

Interface UuidValue<I extends com.google.protobuf.Message>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of the message
    All Superinterfaces:
    com.google.protobuf.Message, com.google.protobuf.MessageLite, com.google.protobuf.MessageLiteOrBuilder, com.google.protobuf.MessageOrBuilder, java.io.Serializable, SerializableMessage

    @Immutable
public interface UuidValue<I extends com.google.protobuf.Message>
extends SerializableMessage
    A common interface for the string-based unique identifiers.

    The messages of suitable format are spotted by the Spine Model Compiler and marked with this interface automatically.

    By convention, a string-based identifier should have exactly one string field named 'uuid': 

         

         message ProjectId {
             // UUID-based generated value.
             string uuid = 1;
         }
